channel.title: Anyone want my 9m on EOC?
channel.description:
I currently quit EOC to pursue my expedition on RS2007, I will greatly miss EOC Runescape but I feel its no longer fun and the RSGP could be put to better use. I have made a new account and now going to only be a RS2007 player. I'm giving my 9m away to the first person to contact me, its a first come first serve policy. I'm giving it away for in return maybe a RS MEMBERSHIP 30day card in hopes. If you can donate that to me for the rsgp it will be great, well, hope to hear from someone soon.
Email me: heyimsimon@gmail.com
Facebook: www.facebook.com/simonlatchford
RS MEMBERSHIP CARD 30 DAY
